  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00001",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "苦啊！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00002",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "无情天，他他他，他他他，偏把俺，生作女儿身，三江水洗不去这妖狐名。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00003",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯披发上，跌倒。丫鬟上，扶晴雯起。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00004",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "悔当初万不该烂漫天真。悔当初万不该嫉恶太甚，悔当初万不该以礼节，清到而今，害得我冤屈莫伸，纵死在九泉下目也不瞑。",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00005",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "丫鬟"
      ],
      "text": "啊，晴雯姑娘，病中被逐，到底为了何事？何不见过老太太，赔罪认过央告几句。她老夫人家发个慈悲，天大的事，也就完了，在此悲伤何益。",
      "text_length": 63
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00006",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "妹妹，你说哪里话来。想俺晴雯，在大观园中，独往独来，从不仰人鼻息，我本无过，央告什么？我本无罪，何用慈悲？我们不幸生作女儿，又作侍婢，真是不幸中之不幸，只要问心无愧，正当抖擞精神，为我女儿家，留点身分，莫玷污了“女儿”这两个字。正是：",
      "text_length": 117
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00007",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "一点贞心照千古，不向东风浪折腰。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00008",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "说什么堂前苦哀告，说什么赔罪折纤腰。我只自问无愧怍，留取气节作女豪。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00009",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "丫鬟"
      ],
      "text": "啊，晴雯姑娘，既不肯去见老太太，何不见过宝二爷，说说离情，也是你二人，相处了一场。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00010",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯惊。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00011",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "噢，那宝玉么，哎，我是不见他的了。啊，我是不能见他的了，啊，啊，啊。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00012",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯、丫鬟同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00013",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾宝玉上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00014",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "愿作护花主，平生一片心。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00015",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "俺，贾宝玉。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00016",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "焙茗抢上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00017",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "焙茗"
      ],
      "text": "报报报，二爷大事不好了！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00018",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "啊，焙茗，何事如此惊慌？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00019",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "焙茗"
      ],
      "text": "晴雯姑娘，不知为了何事，被太太立时逐出园去。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00020",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "你待怎讲？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00021",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "焙茗"
      ],
      "text": "晴雯姑娘，逐出园去！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00022",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾宝玉拭泪，搓手。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00023",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "有这等事么？呀吓不好了！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00024",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "听说逐出小晴雯，好似钢刀刺我心。恼恨情天何太狠，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00025",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "晴雯姐姐！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00026",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "无限心领痛冤沉。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00027",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "呀，焙茗，不知晴雯被逐，究竟为了何事，现在何处，你可知道？",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00028",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "焙茗"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，二爷，晴雯姑娘，乃是园中最矫激，有气节的女儿，此番被逐，定是被那姐妹们，谗诉所中，一个逐令一下，刻不容留，就回家去了。啊，啊，啊。",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00029",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "如此说来，你与我悄悄备马，由便门出园，速去速去！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00030",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "焙茗"
      ],
      "text": "是，晓得。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00031",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "焙茗下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00032",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "啊，晴雯姐姐呀！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00033",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "贾宝玉下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00034",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯嫂嫂扶晴雯病装同上。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00035",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "反二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "一日别离一日心，病魂犹绕大观园。多情公子难相见，“妖狐”二字痛冤沉。再不能怡红闻夜宴，再不能扯扇掷千金，再不能病补孔雀裘，再不能悄听潇湘琴。",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00036",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "宝玉呵，",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00037",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "反二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "枉费了你一段护花心，要想见除非是这梦里贞魂。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00038",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯嫂嫂推晴雯伏病床，晴雯气郁。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00039",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯嫂嫂"
      ],
      "text": "哼，哼，不得了，姑娘，你不要装斯文了。你自己想想，当日在大观中，何等尊贵，哪一个高攀得上？你多少年儿，从不到娘门上。瞧一瞧你心上的人，又是什么姑娘哩，少爷哩，全不把我们放在眼里，我们常说，贵人是不蹈贱地的了，不料想今日，你还认得家。常言说得好，出了娘家门，还有姨家门，凭姑娘有这个模样儿，宅门上买姨娘娘的，怕买不到手啦，哭什么，瞧好的啵。",
      "text_length": 169
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00040",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯气心痛。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00041",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯嫂嫂"
      ],
      "text": "别撒娇了，我不喜欢那个样儿。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00042",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯怒。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00043",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "你你嫂嫂不羞，敢在我面前来，胡言乱语，还不与我快走出去。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00044",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯嫂嫂"
      ],
      "text": "走可别叫我，我看谁来服侍你，咱斗牌去，阿弥陀佛。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00045",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯嫂嫂下。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00046",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀，天哪天那，想俺晴雯，落得这样地步，不如死了罢！",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00047",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯昏去。贾宝玉、焙茗同上。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00048",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "马上伤情魂欲断，可怜一步一啼痕。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00049",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "焙茗"
      ],
      "text": "来此已是。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00050",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "上前扣门。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00051",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "焙茗"
      ],
      "text": "二爷，门正开着，快快进去罢，免得外人瞧见，传进府去，小子耽待不起。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00052",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "焙茗下，贾宝玉入门，拥晴雯。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00053",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "姐姐醒来。姐姐醒来。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00054",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯见贾宝玉，诧异，双手搓眼细看，欲起不能。贾宝玉扶晴雯起。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00055",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "你怎么来了？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00056",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "我因闻知你被逐，故而急急赶来了。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00057",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯惊异。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00058",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "我敢是做梦呀？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00059",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "明明是我，何言做梦？（晴雯指案上茶壶，贾宝玉斟茶，看，作恶劣。晴雯招手，贾宝玉送茶就晴雯，晴雯举碗抚贾宝玉肩，饮茶。贾宝玉作暗暗下泪。）",
      "text_length": 68
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00060",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "奴只道俺与你此生两参商，忽相见又寸断肝肠。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00061",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "叫奴好喜。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00062",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "喜从何来？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00063",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "喜只喜多情公子重相见，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00064",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "叫奴好恨！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00065",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "恨从何来？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00066",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "恨只恨数年来，朝朝暮暮时时刻刻，都只为，爱惜声名，辜负鸳鸯帐。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00067",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "也罢。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00068",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯咬折手指甲纳贾宝玉荷包内。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00069",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "奴只把这全腔心血交付你，再相见惟有是梦里高唐。你与奴把衣裳互换，",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00070",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯换衣。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00071",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "生同室死同穴只有这件旧衣裳。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00072",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贾宝玉"
      ],
      "text": "啊，姐姐，被逐出园，因何而起？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00073",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯气急。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00074",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "噢，你问我这出园吗？咳，你乃好糊涂，贾二爷，呦，呦，呦，呦。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00075",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "仙女暗上，晴雯嫂嫂、焙茗同上，作掩。贾宝玉作惊慌闪躲。晴雯气绝，仙女暗下。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00076",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯嫂嫂"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，小宝贝人一市，诳狗咬利空，怪不得我……死去活来，今天大好运气，不料想这阵，到我怀里来了，我看宝贝，你往哪里跑。⑴",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00077",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯嫂嫂与贾宝玉扭扯，五儿上。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00078",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "五儿"
      ],
      "text": "晴雯姑娘，可好些了？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00079",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯嫂嫂惊，出迎。贾宝玉逃脱，下。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00080",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯嫂嫂"
      ],
      "text": "我们姑娘好些了，你要他，随我来。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00081",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00082",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯宫装手执姑子上。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00083",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "俺乃晴雯灵魂是也。警幻仙姑怜俺玉洁冰霜，无罪被逐。封俺为芙蓉花神，今有神瑛使者，情缘未了，撰成芙蓉诔文，在大观园中，池边相招。你看今宵，月白风清，不免消遣则个前去。正是：",
      "text_length": 85
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00084",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "晴雯"
      ],
      "text": "情丝不断死犹生，赚煞天离离恨人。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01032006_e00085",
      "play_id": "01032006",
      "scene_id": "01032006_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "晴雯下。——————————⑴原文残缺。",
      "text_length": 20
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}